  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"spell-description\">\n  <p>\n    <strong>School</strong>&nbsp;abjuration;\n    <strong>Level</strong>&nbsp;psychic 5;\n    \n    \n    \n    \n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Casting Time</strong>&nbsp;1 immediate<br>\n    <strong>Components</strong>&nbsp;V<br>\n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Range</strong>&nbsp;personal<br>\n    \n    <strong>Targets</strong>&nbsp;you<br>\n    \n    <strong>Duration</strong>&nbsp;1 round<br>\n    \n  </p>\n  <h2>Description</h2>\n  <p>This spell functions as <i>mental barrier <i>II</i>I</i>, but if you are struck by a critical hit or sneak attack, there is a 25% chance that the additional damage is negated (as <i>light</i> fortification). This does not stack with similar effects that negate the additional damage from a critical hit or sneak attack. In addition, you are immune to <i>mind thrust I</i> and <i>II</i>, and you take half damage from <i>mind thrust I</i><i>II</i>, <i>I<i>V</i></i>, and <i>V</i> (reduced to one-quarter on a successful Will save). This spell can be undercast.</p>\n</div>\n",
